    'description' => 'Import CSV data directly into a SQLite database table with automatic column type detection (INTEGER, REAL, TEXT). Parses CSV with proper quote handling, sanitizes column names for SQLite, and inserts all rows in a single transaction. Composes csv_table parsing with sqlite_query storage in one pipeline. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
